# api/lib/* are shared helper modules, imported by the real endpoints. They
# export no handler and can never serve a request, but Vercel turns every file
# under api/ into a Serverless Function - which burned 4 of the 12 Hobby slots
# and made arc-quote the 13th, so it silently 404'd on a green build.
#
# Ignoring them here stops the function being CREATED. The imports still work:
# the bundler traces `import ... from './lib/oddsEngine.mjs'` and includes the
# code inside each function that needs it.
api/lib/**
